<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Just a question or two relating to the spec DD for sorcerers.  I recently made sixth level with my sorc on Merlin.  I've gone full Body spec so far.  The delve (shift I) for mind jolt shows 20 damage.  That is pretty consistent with the damage that I'm doing to blues and yellows.  However, with my runemaster on the Galahad server I usually do alot more damage to yellows and blues with my dark spec DD than the damage shown with the delve command.  I'm not including critical hits either.  For instance, the delve for rune of murk shows 62 DD, but I usually hit blues and yellows for 90 to 100.  That's not with critical hits or any type of bonuses.  Does the body spec DD not work in the same manner?  Any help would be appreciated.  Thanks in advance to anyone that responds.<P>Variable
</FONT>
