<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
It does work the same way.  One thing to consider is whether you are fighting mobs that you have a bonus to.  Try finding some undead to fight, and you will be much more satisfied with your damage.<P>Also, as you take Body spec up, you minimum damage will increase from that base damage.  I did not try to get the Body spec nuke until later in my career, so I am not sure if what you are seeing is a common occurance at that level.  But I do know that at level 37, using the 22 spec nuke, I consistantly hit for more than the stated damage.<P>--------------------<P><B>Lydon Sharpe</B>-Level 41 Mercenary<BR><B>Gyles</B>-Level 37 Sorcerer<BR>Defenders of the Mithril Tower<BR>Galahad Server
</FONT>
